    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001127.4",
      "line_range": "4",
      "translation": "(ii 1') For Šul-šagana he built the Kitušakkile , and built the Bursaĝ , his house from which the regular offerings are delivered for him ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001127.11",
      "line_range": "11",
      "translation": "(iii 1') For Enlil , he built the Adda in Imsaĝ . For Ninĝirsu he dug her beloved canal , the Pa-Saman-kaša ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001127.20",
      "line_range": "20",
      "translation": "(iv 1') ... Iri-kagina , king of Lagaš , ...."
    }
  ],
